bioSpec.description:
Patients and controls at baseline:

1 x 2.7 mL + 1 x 9ml sodium citrate tube, aliquoted in 4 x 1000 µL cryovials;

1 x 5 mL serum tube, aliquoted in 3 x 500 µL sterile cryovials;

1 x 3 mL EDTA tube, aliquoted in 3 x 500 µL cryovials;

For 20 patients and 20 controls from the Radboudumc the following tubes were addionally collected for whole blood analysis:

1x 2.7 ml citrate tube 3 x 10 ml EDTA tube for PBMCs isolation and storage.

Patients at 3-month visit:

1 x 2.7 mL + 1 x 9ml sodium citrate tube, aliquoted in 4 x 1000 µL cryovials;

1 x 5 mL serum tube, aliquoted in 3 x 500 µL sterile cryovials;

1 x 3 mL EDTA tube, aliquoted in 3 x 500 µL cryovials;

For 20 patients and 20 controls from the Radboudumc the following tubes were addionally collected for whole blood analysis:

1x 2.7 ml citrate tube 3 x 10 ml EDTA tube for PBMCs isolation and storage.
